metadata.description: Windchime is a collection of 2,000 interactive music players, each with unique art. On any NFT, click a circle to start making your own track. Art and music by Mike Shinoda. Built by Secret Garden. Visit https://secretgarden.fm to record and share your own mixes. This collection is a companion to Mikeâ€™s collection ZIGGURATS, the first generative NFT mixtape. More information at https://ziggurats.xyz. License terms at https://www.mikeshinoda.com/NFTTerms
